summary: Adds a weight slider to Julia Jeans CBBEv3
descriptionHtml:
Minor tweak to add a weight slider to Julia jeans. This is not a final product as any weight in between the two extremes is still a little off.

Needed
Original file: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18840

Thanks to
JackGa for the amazing original file
Nightasy for his series of tutorials on 3D modeling in Skyrim: http://www.youtube.com/user/NightasyTutorials/videos
author: Thineubaut
